# CronAI Configuration Example
# Format: timestamp model prompt response_processor [template] [variables]

# Basic configuration without template
0 8 * * * claude product_manager slack-pm-channel

# Configuration with template
0 9 * * * claude system_health slack-alerts system_alert

# Configuration with template and variables
0 9 1 * * claude report_template email-team@company.com monthly_report reportType=Monthly,date={{CURRENT_DATE}},project=CronAI

# Configuration for webhook with custom template
0 */2 * * * openai monitoring_check webhook-monitoring monitoring_alert

# Configuration for file output with template
0 12 * * * gemini weekly_report log-to-file weekly_report_file